Death doesn’t stay buried for long.
In WE BURY THE DEAD (2026), a devastating outbreak unleashes the next evolution of the undead. As cities fall and the infected grow more intelligent — faster, stronger, and relentless — one team must fight through the chaos to uncover the truth behind the resurrection.

Packed with intense action, terrifying zombie set pieces, and gritty survival moments, this 4K Final Trailer delivers the most explosive look yet at the upcoming zombie blockbuster of 2026.
